OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bills to soar 50%   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funless government          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fintervenes, industry warns 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy bills will soar another 50% next
OL,6, year unless the government intervenes, 
OL,7, the industry has warned.               
OL,9,FSupplier EDF said the situation was    
OL,10,F"critical" as customers, already seeing
OL,11,Frecord bills, are hit with more rises  
OL,12,Fdue to surging wholesale gas prices.   
OL,14,FEmma Pinchbeck, head of trade body     
OL,15,FUKEnergy, said rising prices were now  
OL,16,Fstarting to hurt the economy.          
OL,18,FThe government said it had measures to 
OL,19,Fprotect consumers, but she told the BBC
OL,20,Ftax cuts and green levies would help.  
